description: Move right into this sun-drenched spacious 2 bed 2 bath condo in South Boston. Enjoy everything this open floor plan has to offer. An updated kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and modern fixtures opens up to an oversized living and dining space, perfect for entertaining. Go to sleep at night in your king-sized primary suite featuring a massive walk-in closet with a California Closet system and an en suite bath with a rainfall shower, radiant floors, and double vanity. The comfortable queen-sized second bedroom includes a large closet and its own updated full bath right outside its door. Relax outside after a long day on your very own patio space. Additional features include hardwood floors throughout, laundry in unit, Sonos surround sound, ample storage space, and one garage parking space. Just blocks to Southie's restaurants, parks, beaches, and a short distance to both downtown and the Seaport.
